OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,FTeams of experts will be deployed to
OL,7,FNHS trusts with the highest rates of
OL,8,Fcorridor care in a bid to end the
OL,9,F"unacceptable, undignified" practice,
OL,10,Fthe government has announced.
OL,12,FThe worst-offending trusts will be
OL,13,Fgiven help to understand data better
OL,14,Fand improve patient flow, as ministers
OL,15,Faim to eradicate corridor care by the
OL,16,Fend of Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
