PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,FUnder the new initiative, the Getting
OL,7,Fit Right First Time (Girft) team will
OL,8,Fwork with leaders at the worst
OL,9,Foffending NHS trusts to offer support
OL,10,Fon improving patient flow, and
OL,11,Funderstanding data to cope better with
OL,12,Fsurges in demand.
OL,14,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,15,F"For too long, the normalisation of
OL,16,Fcorridor care has been baked into our
OL,17,FNHS ` it's unacceptable, undignified
OL,18,Fand exactly why this government is
OL,19,Fshifting the dial for patients and
OL,20,Fstaff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,F"We're sending in specialist teams of
OL,7,Fexperts to identify the causes in some
OL,8,Fof the worst offending trusts and
OL,9,Fswiftly rectify the problems they
OL,10,Ffind."
OL,12,FMr Streeting made the announcement
OL,13,Fduring a visit to Queen's Hospital in
OL,14,FRomford, which has provided 10,000
OL,15,Ffewer hours of corridor care in
OL,16,FFebruary than in the same month last
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
