CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,FThe hospital's emergency department
OL,7,Fhas introduced a new assessment
OL,8,Fprocess which has cut waiting times by
OL,9,F37 minutes.
OL,11,FElsewhere, in Blackpool, 12-hour waits
OL,12,Fhave fallen by 43%, driven by senior
OL,13,Fstaff being present in A&E and using
OL,14,Fdata to predict busy periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
