FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,FIn Hull, ambulance handover delays are
OL,7,Fdown by 27% and 12-hour waits have
OL,8,Ffallen by 47%, while the Royal
OL,9,FBlackburn in East Lancashire has cut
OL,10,Fcorridor care by allowing the medical
OL,11,Fdirector and chief nurse to take over
OL,12,Fprioritising the patients who should
OL,13,Fbe sent home first.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
