PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776038571
OL,3,CExpert teams to be sent to hospitals
OL,4,Cwith highest rates of corridor care
OL,6,FProfessor Tim Briggs, NHS England's
OL,7,Fnational director for clinical
OL,8,Fimprovement, elective and UEC
OL,9,Frecovery, and chair of the Girft
OL,10,Fprogramme, said: "We have worked
OL,11,Falongside these trusts to produce
OL,12,Fguidance and standards, as well as
OL,13,Fproviding hands-on support, which will
OL,14,Fhelp them significantly reduce
OL,15,Fcorridor care.
OL,17,F"Our focus over the next six months is
OL,18,Fto take what we've learned and cascade
OL,19,Fit across the whole NHS, so we can
OL,20,Fimprove care for patients and
OL,21,Feliminate this issue once and for all."
OL,26,@rD@ROUyD@AOU}D@gO]
